{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_04_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫 2話 ドルオタの名に懸けて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、かっこ良くなるために\n今日から特訓する……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ in order to become cooler‚\nWe're starting special training today…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで、特訓って何をすればいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…By the way‚ what should we do for special training?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺に聞かれても困るが……そうだな……\nかっこいい言葉を言ってみるのはどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's kind of difficult for me to answer… but‚ well…\nHow about trying to say cool words?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういうセリフを言う時は\n自然と顔つきもかっこ良くなるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you say lines like that‚\nyour facial expression might naturally become cooler.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、やってみる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it‚ I'll give it a try…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "――初めての挫折を、私達が味わわせてあげる\n……キリッ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――We will make you taste your first failure…\n…Sharp!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……どう、かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ what do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんというか……微妙だな……\nもしかして、今のは莉央さんの真似か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's kind of… subtle…\nWas that just an imitation of Rio?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "そう。莉央さんをイメージしてみた……\nかっこいいと言えば、リズノワだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I tried to imagine Rio…\nSince LizNoir is cool when they speak cool lines…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、アイドル好きな雫らしいな\nでもここは別の言葉にした方がいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ that's very much like you‚ who loves idols.\nBut shouldn't you try using different words?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。違う言葉にする……\nそれじゃあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it. I'll use different words…\nThen…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "――僕はカニカマとずるいことは嫌いなんだ\n……キリッ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――I dislike crab sticks and unfair things…!\n…Sharp!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "……どう、かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ what do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "葵の真似になっただけじゃないか\nそれに、いちいちキメ顔しないといけないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like you just imitated Aoi.\nBesides‚ do you have to make a determined expression every time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "これもダメ……？　難しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this not good either…? It's tough…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、かっこいいって何……？\n見た目……？　仕草……？　雰囲気……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ what does it mean to be cool…?\nAppearance…? Gestures…? Atmosphere…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "それが分からないと、特訓にならない……\nもっと勉強しないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I don't understand that‚ this won't become special training…\nI need to study more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、勉強するって……一体どうしたら……\n……はっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But studying… how on earth…\n…Ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7566.666666699987,
          "startTime": 104.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "そういう人を観察して極意を学ぶ……\nうん、それがいい……ちょっと観察して来る……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Observe people like that and learn their secrets…\nYeah‚ that's a good idea… I'll observe a bit…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、雫！？\n……観察するって、何をするつもりだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ Shizuku!?\n…Observing‚ what exactly are you planning to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "雫のやつ、どこに行ったんだ？\n……ん？　あれはスリクスか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where did that Shizuku go?\n…Hm? Is that IIIX?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
