      "text": "だから隠れて観察してる……\n先輩の仕事を見て、技術を盗む……それがプロ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I'm watching from hiding…\nWatching a senpai's work and learning techniques… That's what being a pro is…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8,
      "sfxList": []
